    "# Exploratory Data Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "## Overview\n",
    "\n",
    "This page explores the cleaned Lightcast job postings dataset created during the data preparation step. The purpose of this exploratory analysis is to understand the dataset size, salary availability, missing salary patterns, remote-work categories, geographic concentration, industry concentration, occupation mix, and skill demand before moving into the main salary analysis.\n",
