   "source": [
    "**Key insight:** Salary varies across both education levels and occupation categories. Higher education groups generally show higher salary ranges, while occupation categories such as Enterprise Architect, Oracle Consultant / Analyst, and General ERP Analyst / Consultant show different median salaries and wider salary spreads than some analyst-focused roles. This suggests that compensation is strongly connected to role type and qualification level.\n",
    "\n",
    "## 7. Remote Work Type Distribution\n",
    "\n",
    "Why this visualization was chosen:  \n",
    "Remote-work type is an important job characteristic, but it may contain unclear categories. This chart shows whether remote-work status is clearly captured in the dataset."
