   "source": [
    "**Key insight:** Remote-work status is not clearly identified for most postings, with [None] representing the largest category. This category should be treated as a data-quality issue rather than a true work arrangement. Clearly labeled categories such as Remote, Hybrid Remote, and Not Remote are more reliable for later salary comparisons.\n",
    "\n",
    "## 8. Top States by Job Postings\n",
    "\n",
    "Why this visualization was chosen:  \n",
    "Location can affect salary and labor-market demand. This chart shows where job postings are most concentrated geographically."
   ]
