   "source": [
    "**Key insight:** Job postings are concentrated in a small number of states, especially Texas and California. These high-volume states provide stronger sample sizes for geographic analysis, while smaller markets may produce less stable salary or demand comparisons.\n",
    "\n",
    "## 9. Top Industries by Job Postings\n",
    "\n",
    "Why this visualization was chosen:  \n",
    "Industry context helps identify which sectors contribute the most job postings. This matters because salary availability and job characteristics may differ by industry."
   ]
