    "**Key insight:** Job postings are concentrated in unclassified industry, computer programming, management consulting, employment agencies, and computer systems design. The large unclassified industry category shows that industry-level analysis should be interpreted carefully because not all postings have a clearly defined sector.\n",
    "\n",
    "## 10. Occupation Categories\n",
    "\n",
    "Why this visualization was chosen:  \n",
    "Occupation is an important job characteristic because salary and required skills may differ across analyst, architect, ERP, Oracle, SAP, business analyst, and BI roles."
