    "**Key insight:** The dataset is heavily concentrated in Data Analyst roles, followed by ERP Analyst / Consultant, Enterprise Architect, Oracle Consultant / Analyst, and SAP Analyst / Admin roles. This shows that the dataset is not evenly balanced across occupations and that later salary analysis may be influenced by the dominance of data analyst postings.\n",
    "\n",
    "## 11. Top Skills in Job Postings\n",
    "\n",
    "Why this visualization was chosen:  \n",
    "Skills describe what employers request in each posting. A top-skills visualization helps identify which technical, analytical, software, and business skills appear most often."
